CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: INmune Bio Inc is a clinical-stage biotechnology company. It is engaged in the development of new immunotherapies that reprogram a patient's innate immune system to allow the immune system to fight cancer. The company's pipeline products includeINKmune, INBO3, XPro1595, LIVNate, and others.
